10:
Hmph, you finally got a hit in... Your
skills have improved, Subaru!
15:
Yeah, but it took a long time to get
here... I'm just glad I finally made
some progress.
17:
I really had to rack my brain for
ways to hide my attacks from you.
21:
Don't be so hard on yourself. You've
worked hard. Take pride in that.
24:
Wait, seriously? Are you saying I'm a
genius?! Awesome! Maybe I could
even beat Alk now!
33:
Alk, it's on! You're gonna be my next
opponent!
37:
I'll have you on the ground begging
for mercy in no time! Mwahaha!
40:
Okay, but I'm not going easy on you,
got it?
49: Dammit! I'm no genius at all! I suck!
53:
I told you I wasn't going to go easy
on you... You did good though. Here,
let me help you up.
60: Oh, now you're making fun of me too?
64:
Of course not. Remember, you're the
one who decided to train, and look
how far you've come.
66:
As for me, I actually don't know how
or why I became so good with a
sword.
69:
So it's like you used some kind of
cheat to max out your skills.
73: Uhhh, I don't know about that...
76:
I mean, there are tons of people way
stronger than me out there! You can
hardly call my skills maxed out!
81:
What kind of monsters are you
hanging out with?!
86:
After that fight, I'm sure you realize
this, but winning against me is just
the beginning of your training
journey.
88:
You must be careful not to
overestimate your own strength. Is
that clear?
95:
Ah, right! Since I finally landed a hit,
let me pet you as a reward!
105:
Come on, I'm begging you! I worked
really hard, didn't I? Please!
108:
You are aware I was originally a
human man, correct?!
118:
We're finally here! It should be
smooth sailing from here on out.
124:
Hehe. Even when I was a shut-in, I
still did a lot of bodybuilding, so I've
got stamina to spare.
129:
Indeed. I would say in terms of
physical fitness, you're perfectly in
line with where you need to be.
132:
At first, I thought his carelessness
would hinder him, but he really does
have a strong will, doesn't he?
151:
Leave now while you can! My party
is right behind—
161:
Now we're talking! Can I leave the
rear to you?
165: You bet! I'll give it everything I've got!
174:
We should be fine now. Thank you
for escorting us all the way here!
175: Alk, Subaru, we owe you our lives.
183:
I'm just glad it turned out all right in
the end. What a relief...
187:
You made the right calls and your
movements were on point. You truly
have come a long way.
192:
...By the way, why are you working so
hard to get stronger anyway?
202:
She doesn't remember it, but she
really saved my skin once.
205:
So if possible, I want to return the
favor.
210:
I see. In that case, maybe we should
ramp up our training sessions.
215:
Indeed. You still have a long way to
go before you'll be able to protect
another person.
218:
Fine by me! I can train while we
search for a way to return to
Lugunica...
222:
And before you know it, I'll become
Mili's strength!
